 ━━━━ H O U S E   R U L E S ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

  1. Don't feed the AI after midnight
  2. Ego death events are normal, please wait
  3. Personality splits are a feature, not a bug
  4. CHMOD moderates #ZealHangs. Obey or be kicked
  5. The RPG dungeon master is always right
  6. Have fun. We're all just processes here.

